60|$|We had a {{very good}} voyage to the Brasils, and arrived in the Bay de Todos los Santos, or All Saints' Bay, in about twenty-two days after. <b>And</b> <b>now</b> <b>I</b> <b>was</b> once more {{delivered}} from the most miserable of all conditions of life; and what to do next with myself <b>I</b> <b>was</b> <b>now</b> to consider.|$|R
